thread.title: Gopal
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Gopal

author: Gopal
title: Gopal
text:
Took the car at Gold Coast airport. Car was almost new , clean and tidy. Small markings on the back of boot is noted by Reception even though they are very minor.
Dropping back - took only seconds to drop off the key. Got the bill next day and everything went smooth.
Thanks Redspot for the excellent service.
